CORS cho presigned URL Nếu Admin Console hoặc frontend mở file bằng presigned URL, thêm CORS cho bucket:
[ { &#34;AllowedHeaders&#34;: [&#34;*&#34;], &#34;AllowedMethods&#34;: [&#34;GET&#34;, &#34;PUT&#34;, &#34;POST&#34;], &#34;AllowedOrigins&#34;: [ &#34;http://localhost:5173&#34;, &#34;https://&lt;amplify-domain-cua-ban&gt;&#34; ], &#34;ExposeHeaders&#34;: [&#34;ETag&#34;] } ] IAM policy tối thiểu cho Lambda { &#34;Effect&#34;: &#34;Allow&#34;, &#34;Action&#34;: [&#34;s3:GetObject&#34;, &#34;s3:PutObject&#34;], &#34;Resource&#34;: &#34;arn:aws:s3:::talent-graph-ai-storage-huydat/*&#34; } Nếu Lambda cần liệt kê object:
{ &#34;Effect&#34;: &#34;Allow&#34;, &#34;Action&#34;: [&#34;s3:ListBucket&#34;], &#34;Resource&#34;: &#34;arn:aws:s3:::talent-graph-ai-storage-huydat&#34; }
